column5: For those interested in going to a Buffalo Bills game......  http://www.buffalonews.com/sports/bills-nfl/article624740.ece
They ought to after that Jets game
Ticket sales will be tough for December if the games don't mean anything (out of the playoff picture).  Tom
after such a strong start too what happened?  I still think they can make the playoffs if they stay healthy and brady keeps throwin 2-3 ints a game

Bottom line the Buffalo Bills are pretenders and will be as long as R.W. is the owner...  I just posted this because I know some of you guys are interested....personally I would not go to the game if it was free.   Bob
